00&amp;fit=max&amp;w=1200"/></div></section><section data-slice-type="brand_trust" data-slice-variation="default" class="mb-0"><div class="container mb-5 flex flex-col-reverse items-end justify-between gap-y-6 sm:flex-row sm:gap-y-0"><div class="w-full text-left sm:w-1/3"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="290" height="50" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mx-auto md:mx-0" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-095ndAxsiBwOmf_trustpilot-cookiehub.webp?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=max&amp;w=384 1x, https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-095ndAxsiBwOmf_trustpilot-cookiehub.webp?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=max&amp;w=640 2x" src="https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-095ndAxsiBwOmf_trustpilot-cookiehub.webp?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=max&amp;w=640"/><p class="text-24 mt-6 text-center tracking-tighter sm:mt-2 md:text-left">Trusted and used by 25,000+ websites and companies around the world.</p></div><div class="w-full sm:w-2/3"><div class="mx-auto flex max-w-lg flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 sm:max-w-xl md:justify-end lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:flex-row"><img alt="" src="https://cookiehub-web.cdn.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-09nXdAxsiBwOl3_monday.svg" width="158" height="48" class="h-full max-h-6 w-auto object-contain opacity-45 grayscale transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-100 hover:grayscale-0 sm:max-h-9"/><img alt="" src="https://cookiehub-web.cdn.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-091XdAxsiBwOmV_semrush.svg" width="158" height="48" class="h-full max-h-6 w-auto object-contain opacity-45 grayscale transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-100 hover:grayscale-0 sm:max-h-9"/><img alt="" src="https://cookiehub-web.cdn.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-091HdAxsiBwOmU_dealfront.svg" width="158" height="48" class="h-full max-h-6 w-auto object-contain opacity-45 grayscale transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-100 hover:grayscale-0 sm:max-h-9"/><img alt="" src="https://cookiehub-web.cdn.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-091ndAxsiBwOmW_tixly.svg" width="158" height="48" class="h-full max-h-6 w-auto object-contain opacity-45 grayscale transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-100 hover:grayscale-0 sm:max-h-9"/></div></div></div></section><div data-slice-type="divider" data-slice-variation="default" class="divider container mx-auto"></div><section data-slice-type="title" data-slice-variation="default" class=""><div class="container"><div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-x-10 gap-y-4 lg:flex-row lg:gap-y-0"><div class="w-full lg:w-1/2"><h3 class="text-32 lg:text-56 mr-8">You don’t need to be a privacy expert</h3></div><div class="w-full lg:w-1/2"><p class="text-18 mb-4">Staying up to date with growing data privacy regulations and handling cookie consent with a cumbersome tool takes valuable time away from designing, developing, and optimising your websites and platforms. Cookiehub provides peace of mind that your websites become and remain compliant, so you can focus on doing your job.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-slice-type="feature_highlights" data-slice-variation="default" class=""><div class="container-wide"><div class="mx-auto w-full text-center md:w-3/4"></div><div class="grid gap-x-16 gap-y-12 col-span-1 mt-4 !gap-x-6 md:mt-14 md:grid-cols-3"><div role="contentinfo" aria-label="Seamless integration" class="flex flex-col rounded-xl bg-white p-8 shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200 ease-in-out hover:shadow-lg"><svg viewBox="0 0 43 39" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-11 w-11 sm:h-[50px] sm:w-[50px] text-primary-100 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M15.3213 30.9326H4.32129M10.3213 19.9326H1.32129M15.3213 8.93262H5.32129M31.3213 1.93262L18.1284 20.4026C17.5445 21.2201 17.2525 21.6289 17.2652 21.9697C17.2762 22.2664 17.4184 22.5428 17.6535 22.7243C17.9235 22.9326 18.4258 22.9326 19.4304 22.9326H29.3213L27.3213 37.9326L40.5142 19.4626C41.0981 18.6451 41.3901 18.2364 41.3774 17.8956C41.3664 17.5989 41.2241 17.3224 40.9891 17.141C40.7191 16.9326 40.2168 16.9326 39.2122 16.9326H29.3213L31.3213 1.93262Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><h3 class="text-20 lg:text-26 mt-3 mb-3 lg:mt-6 lg:mb-4 lg:!font-normal">Seamless integration</h3><p class="text-14 lg:text-18">Just a few clicks away from easily setting up your cookie consent widget.</p></div><div role="contentinfo" aria-label="Customizable" class="flex flex-col rounded-xl bg-white p-8 shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200 ease-in-out hover:shadow-lg"><svg viewBox="0 0 42 42" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-11 w-11 sm:h-[50px] sm:w-[50px] text-primary-100 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M15.3544 18.9848L22.91 26.5404M13.3042 38.4901C10.5705 41.2238 5.35449 40.5404 1.35449 40.5404C3.40469 36.5404 0.671022 31.3243 3.40469 28.5906C6.13836 25.857 10.5705 25.857 13.3042 28.5906C16.0379 31.3243 16.0379 35.7565 13.3042 38.4901ZM21.1977 28.3896L39.4719 8.65346C41.0815 6.91514 41.0296 4.21557 39.3544 2.54038C37.6792 0.865199 34.9796 0.813299 33.2413 2.42286L13.5052 20.6971C12.4853 21.6414 11.9754 22.1136 11.6779 22.6171C10.9648 23.8247 10.9361 25.3175 11.6023 26.5515C11.8801 27.0661 12.3716 27.5576 13.3544 28.5404C14.3372 29.5232 14.8286 30.0146 15.3432 30.2925C16.5773 30.9587 18.0701 30.93 19.2776 30.2168C19.7812 29.9194 20.2534 29.4095 21.1977 28.3896Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><h3 class="text-20 lg:text-26 mt-3 mb-3 lg:mt-6 lg:mb-4 lg:!font-normal">Customizable</h3><p class="text-14 lg:text-18">Choose between various themes, style buttons, colours and placement of the widget shown on your website.</p></div><div role="contentinfo" aria-label="Peace of mind" class="flex flex-col rounded-xl bg-white p-8 shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200 ease-in-out hover:shadow-lg"><svg viewBox="0 0 43 43" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-11 w-11 sm:h-[50px] sm:w-[50px] text-primary-100 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M41.1992 21.7373H37.1992M35.3411 35.8795L32.5127 33.051M5.19922 21.7373H1.19922M9.88507 10.4236L7.05664 7.59521M21.1992 5.7373V1.7373M32.5127 10.4236L35.3411 7.59521M21.1992 41.7373V37.7373M7.05664 35.8795L9.88507 33.051M21.1992 11.7373L24.2892 17.9973L31.1992 19.0073L26.1992 23.8773L27.3792 30.7573L21.1992 27.5073L15.0192 30.7573L16.1992 23.8773L11.1992 19.0073L18.1092 17.9973L21.1992 11.7373Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><h3 class="text-20 lg:text-26 mt-3 mb-3 lg:mt-6 lg:mb-4 lg:!font-normal">Peace of mind</h3><p class="text-14 lg:text-18">Ensuring you are following ever-changing cookie privacy regulations around the world.</p></div></div><div class="col-span-1 mt-6 flex justify-center sm:col-span-3 sm:mt-12"><a href="/product"><button type="button" class="border-primary-100 bg-primary-100 border text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:outline-none hover:text-primary-100 focus:ring-primary-100 hover:bg-white bg-primary-100 uppercase rounded-md px-[25px] py-[12px] text-sm relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start">Explore all of the features</button></a></div></div></section><section data-slice-type="image" data-slice-variation="default" class="container flex flex-col items-center text-center"><h2 class="text-[30px] lg:text-[42px]">Regulations Worldwide</h2><div class="my-14 w-full"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="700" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1032px]" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-5t6ndAxsiBwRNJ_cookiehub-regulations-worldwide.png.webp?q=100&amp;fit=max&amp;w=1200 1x, https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-5t6ndAxsiBwRNJ_cookiehub-regulations-worldwide.png.webp?q=100&amp;fit=max&amp;w=3840 2x" src="https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-5t6ndAxsiBwRNJ_cookiehub-regulations-worldwide.png.webp?q=100&amp;fit=max&amp;w=3840"/></div><a href="/regulations"><button type="button" class="border-primary-100 bg-primary-100 border text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:outline-none hover:text-primary-100 focus:ring-primary-100 hover:bg-white bg-primary-100 uppercase rounded-md px-[25px] py-[12px] text-sm relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start">Explore Locations</button></a></section><section data-slice-type="feature_spotlight" data-slice-variation="default" class="relative overflow-hidden section-gradient"><div class="container"><div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-x-24 lg:flex-row lg:items-center"><div class="mt-8 w-full lg:mt-0 lg:w-2/5"><img src="https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-5pDXdAxsiBwRJe_implement-platforms.png.webp?auto=format,compress" width="900" height="842" class="mx-auto h-auto w-auto animate-forward"/></div><div class="mt-8 flex w-full flex-col px-2 lg:mt-0 lg:w-3/5 lg:px-0"><h2 class="text-32 lg:text-48 font-600">Simply works with your favourite platforms.</h2><div class="mt-6 mb-3"><p class="text-20 mb-4">Integrating CookieHub with your favourite website builder or CMS is a seamless process and one we help guide you through.</p><p class="text-20 mb-4">CookieHub is tightly integrated with Google Tag Manager (GTM) and automatically sends triggers based on actions made in the CookieHub widget.</p></div><div class="mb-4 flex flex-col items-start gap-x-16 gap-y-4 lg:mb-0 lg:flex-row"></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:justify-start"><a href="/implementation"><button type="button" class="text-primary-100 border-transparent bg-transparent hover:text-secondary-100 bg-primary-100 rounded-md px-[25px] py-[12px] text-sm !p-0 !text-base md:!text-lg relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start text-primary-100 group"><p class="mr-1">How to implement CookieHub</p><svg viewBox="0 0 25 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-100 group-hover:text-secondary-100 mt-1 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M8.67279 18.0303C8.3799 17.7374 8.3799 17.2626 8.67279 16.9697L14.3925 11.25L8.6728 5.53033C8.3799 5.23744 8.3799 4.76256 8.6728 4.46967C8.96569 4.17678 9.44056 4.17678 9.73346 4.46967L15.9835 10.7197C16.2763 11.0126 16.2763 11.4874 15.9835 11.7803L9.73346 18.0303C9.44056 18.3232 8.96569 18.3232 8.67279 18.0303Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></button></a><a href="/wordpress"><button type="button" class="text-primary-100 border-transparent bg-transparent hover:text-secondary-100 bg-primary-100 rounded-md px-[25px] py-[12px] text-sm !p-0 !text-base md:!text-lg relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start text-primary-100 group"><p class="mr-1">WordPress Plugin</p><svg viewBox="0 0 25 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-100 group-hover:text-secondary-100 mt-1 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M8.67279 18.0303C8.3799 17.7374 8.3799 17.2626 8.67279 16.9697L14.3925 11.25L8.6728 5.53033C8.3799 5.23744 8.3799 4.76256 8.6728 4.46967C8.96569 4.17678 9.44056 4.17678 9.73346 4.46967L15.9835 10.7197C16.2763 11.0126 16.2763 11.4874 15.9835 11.7803L9.73346 18.0303C9.44056 18.3232 8.96569 18.3232 8.67279 18.0303Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></button></a></div></div></div></div></section><section data-slice-type="feature_card" data-slice-variation="default" class="container"><div class="bg-secondary-100 flex flex-col rounded-3xl p-6 text-white lg:p-16"><div class="mb-12 flex flex-col items-center lg:flex-row"><div class="w-full lg:w-1/2"><h3 class="text-40 lg:text-56 font-600">Simple, yet powerful</h3></div><div class="mt-2 w-full lg:mt-0 lg:w-1/2"><p class="text-16">Take control of your cookie privacy with confidence. Explore our features designed for simplicity and built for reliability.</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-x-16 gap-y-8 lg:flex-row"><div role="contentinfo" aria-label="Cookie Scanner" class="flex basis-full flex-col items-center text-center lg:items-start lg:text-left text-center lg:text-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 43 38" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-11 w-11 sm:h-[50px] sm:w-[50px] text-primary-100 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M18.2204 24.761C16.6583 23.1989 16.6583 20.6663 18.2204 19.1042C19.7825 17.5421 22.3152 17.5421 23.8773 19.1042C25.4394 20.6663 25.4394 23.1989 23.8773 24.761M12.5635 30.4179C7.87725 25.7316 7.87725 18.1336 12.5635 13.4473C17.2498 8.76104 24.8478 8.76104 29.5341 13.4473C34.2204 18.1336 34.2204 25.7316 29.5341 30.4179M6.90669 36.0748C-0.903793 28.2643 -0.903794 15.601 6.90669 7.79048C14.7172 -0.0200043 27.3805 -0.0200043 35.191 7.79048C43.0014 15.601 43.0014 28.2643 35.191 36.0748" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><circle cx="21.0488" cy="21.9326" r="5" fill="currentColor"></circle></svg><h3 class="text-20 lg:text-24 mt-2.5 mb-1 lg:!font-normal !font-400">Cookie Scanner</h3><p class="text-base">Scans your website for you and detects the cookies that are in use. Learn more</p></div><div role="contentinfo" aria-label="Cookie Notice" class="flex basis-full flex-col items-center text-center lg:items-start lg:text-left text-center lg:text-left"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" class="h-11 w-11 sm:h-[50px] sm:w-[50px] text-primary-100 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M40 25V13.6C40 10.2397 40 8.55953 39.346 7.27606C38.7708 6.14708 37.8529 5.2292 36.7239 4.65396C35.4405 4 33.7603 4 30.4 4H17.6C14.2397 4 12.5595 4 11.2761 4.65396C10.1471 5.2292 9.2292 6.14708 8.65396 7.27606C8 8.55953 8 10.2397 8 13.6V34.4C8 37.7603 8 39.4405 8.65396 40.7239C9.2292 41.8529 10.1471 42.7708 11.2761 43.346C12.5595 44 14.2397 44 17.6 44H24M28 22H16M20 30H16M32 14H16M29 38L33 42L42 33" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><h3 class="text-20 lg:text-24 mt-2.5 mb-1 lg:!font-normal !font-400">Cookie Notice</h3><p class="text-base">Automatically generates a detailed list of the cookies in use on your site.</p></div><div role="contentinfo" aria-label="Pre-Consent" class="flex basis-full flex-col items-center text-center lg:items-start lg:text-left text-center lg:text-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 37 43" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-11 w-11 sm:h-[50px] sm:w-[50px] text-primary-100 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M21.248 19.124H9.24805M13.248 27.124H9.24805M25.248 11.124H9.24805M33.248 17.124V10.724C33.248 7.36371 33.248 5.68355 32.5941 4.40008C32.0188 3.27111 31.101 2.35322 29.972 1.77798C28.6885 1.12402 27.0084 1.12402 23.648 1.12402H10.848C7.48773 1.12402 5.80757 1.12402 4.5241 1.77798C3.39513 2.35322 2.47725 3.27111 1.90201 4.40008C1.24805 5.68355 1.24805 7.36371 1.24805 10.724V31.524C1.24805 34.8843 1.24805 36.5645 1.90201 37.848C2.47725 38.9769 3.39513 39.8948 4.5241 40.4701C5.80757 41.124 7.48773 41.124 10.848 41.124H18.248M29.248 39.124C29.248 39.124 35.248 36.2642 35.248 31.9745V26.9698L30.8728 25.4064C29.8216 25.0299 28.672 25.0299 27.6208 25.4064L23.248 26.9698V31.9745C23.248 36.2642 29.248 39.124 29.248 39.124Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><h3 class="text-20 lg:text-24 mt-2.5 mb-1 lg:!font-normal !font-400">Pre-Consent</h3><p class="text-base">Gain your customers trust by ensuring their privacy is taken seriously.</p></div></div><div class="mx-auto mt-16 mb-6 w-[275px] lg:mx-0 lg:mt-12 lg:w-auto"><a href="/product"><button type="button" class="border-primary-100 bg-primary-100 border text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:outline-none hover:text-primary-100 focus:ring-primary-100 hover:bg-white bg-primary-100 uppercase !rounded-sm px-6 py-[11px] text-sm relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start">Explore all of the features</button></a></div></div></section><section data-slice-type="comparison_card" data-slice-variation="default" class="container"><h3 class="text-40 font-700">Cookie Consent Management</h3><p class="text-24 mt-4 md:mt-0">Discover how we can help your business</p><div class="mt-8 lg:mt-16"><div class="ml-4 flex justify-between sm:justify-start sm:gap-x-14"><button class="text-24 cursor-pointer lg:text-[28px] text-primary-100" aria-label="Switch to Basic collection" aria-current="true">Basic</button><button class="text-24 cursor-pointer lg:text-[28px] text-secondary-50" aria-label="Switch to Business collection" aria-current="false">Business</button><button class="text-24 cursor-pointer lg:text-[28px] text-secondary-50" aria-label="Switch to Enterprise collection" aria-current="false">Enterprise</button></div><div class="mt-6 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50"><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-0 lg:flex-nowrap" style="opacity:0"><div class="w-full px-6 py-8 lg:px-12 lg:py-16 lg:w-1/2"><h3 class="lg:text-32 font-600 text-24">Fully compliant for only €8 per month</h3><div class="mt-5"><ul class="flex list-none flex-col gap-y-3"><li class="text-16 flex items-center gap-x-3"><svg viewBox="0 0 36 26" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-100 !h-5 !w-5 shrink-0 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M34.5825 1.00536C35.2537 1.67656 35.2537 2.76483 34.5825 3.43604L13.0022 25.0164C12.331 25.6874 11.2428 25.6874 10.5716 25.0164L1.21434 15.6591C0.543136 14.9879 0.543136 13.8996 1.21434 13.2283C1.88555 12.5573 2.97382 12.5573 3.64502 13.2283L11.7869 21.3704L32.1519 1.00536C32.8231 0.334152 33.9112 0.334152 34.5825 1.00536Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Cookie verification ensures compliance after installation</li><li class="text-16 flex items-center gap-x-3"><svg viewBox="0 0 36 26" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-100 !h-5 !w-5 shrink-0 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M34.5825 1.00536C35.2537 1.67656 35.2537 2.76483 34.5825 3.43604L13.0022 25.0164C12.331 25.6874 11.2428 25.6874 10.5716 25.0164L1.21434 15.6591C0.543136 14.9879 0.543136 13.8996 1.21434 13.2283C1.88555 12.5573 2.97382 12.5573 3.64502 13.2283L11.7869 21.3704L32.1519 1.00536C32.8231 0.334152 33.9112 0.334152 34.5825 1.00536Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>With automatic language detection</li><li class="text-16 flex items-center gap-x-3"><svg viewBox="0 0 36 26" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-100 !h-5 !w-5 shrink-0 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M34.5825 1.00536C35.2537 1.67656 35.2537 2.76483 34.5825 3.43604L13.0022 25.0164C12.331 25.6874 11.2428 25.6874 10.5716 25.0164L1.21434 15.6591C0.543136 14.9879 0.543136 13.8996 1.21434 13.2283C1.88555 12.5573 2.97382 12.5573 3.64502 13.2283L11.7869 21.3704L32.1519 1.00536C32.8231 0.334152 33.9112 0.334152 34.5825 1.00536Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Logs each consent for full compliance and total peace of mind!</li></ul></div><div class="mt-12"><a href="/register?product_id=29"><button type="button" class="border-primary-100 bg-primary-100 border text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:outline-none hover:text-primary-100 focus:ring-primary-100 hover:bg-white bg-primary-100 uppercase !rounded-sm px-6 py-[11px] text-sm relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start text-14 rounded-sm uppercase">Start 30 day free trial</button></a></div></div><div class="flex w-full items-end justify-end lg:w-1/2"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="706" height="410" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full object-contain lg:w-[600px]" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/aCXnGidWJ-7kSKNj_browser-plans.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=max&amp;w=750 1x, https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/aCXnGidWJ-7kSKNj_browser-plans.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=max&amp;w=1920 2x" src="https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/aCXnGidWJ-7kSKNj_browser-plans.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=max&amp;w=1920"/></div></div></div></div><div class="text-primary-100 text-18 mt-4 lg:mt-8 lg:ml-8"><a href="/pricing">View detailed pricing and plans</a></div></section><section data-slice-type="call_to_action_card" data-slice-variation="default"><div class="container-wide"><div class="relative rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 p-4 lg:p-16"><div class="absolute -top-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div><div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center lg:mt-0"><h3 class="text-32 font-600">Scan your website for cookies</h3><p class="text-18 px-0 pt-4 lg:px-52">You can check your website for cookies for free by using our cookie scanner tool. We will generate a help report of the cookies currently in use.</p><a class="text-primary-100 text-18 mt-6 pb-6 lg:pb-0" href="/scan-report"><button type="button" class="border-primary-100 bg-primary-100 border text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:outline-none hover:text-primary-100 focus:ring-primary-100 hover:bg-white bg-primary-100 uppercase rounded-md px-[25px] py-[12px] text-sm relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start group hover:text-primary-100 flex items-center gap-x-2 transition-all duration-300">Click here to start</button></a></div></div></div></section><section data-slice-type="feature_spotlight" data-slice-variation="default" class="relative overflow-hidden"><div class="container"><div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-x-24 lg:flex-row lg:items-center"><div class="mt-8 w-full lg:mt-0 lg:w-2/5"><img src="https://images.prismic.io/cookiehub-web/Z-1Y3HdAxsiBwPCj_consent-log-comp-1170x694.webp?auto=format,compress" width="1170" height="694" class="mx-auto h-auto w-auto"/></div><div class="mt-8 flex w-full flex-col px-2 lg:mt-0 lg:w-3/5 lg:px-0"><h3 class="text-32 font-600">Cookie Consent Log</h3><div class="mt-6 mb-3"><p class="text-20 mb-4">When the consent log feature is enabled, CookieHub logs and stores user consents along with necessary information required to look up user choices in case you’ll have to demonstrate consents to authorities. This feature is only available for premium subscriptions.</p></div><div class="mb-4 flex flex-col items-start gap-x-16 gap-y-4 lg:mb-0 lg:flex-row"></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:justify-start"><a href="/consent-log"><button type="button" class="text-primary-100 border-transparent bg-transparent hover:text-secondary-100 bg-primary-100 rounded-md px-[25px] py-[12px] text-sm !p-0 !text-base md:!text-lg relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start text-primary-100 group"><p class="mr-1">More about consent logging</p><svg viewBox="0 0 25 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-primary-100 group-hover:text-secondary-100 mt-1 duration-200 ease-in-out"><path d="M8.67279 18.0303C8.3799 17.7374 8.3799 17.2626 8.67279 16.9697L14.3925 11.25L8.6728 5.53033C8.3799 5.23744 8.3799 4.76256 8.6728 4.46967C8.96569 4.17678 9.44056 4.17678 9.73346 4.46967L15.9835 10.7197C16.2763 11.0126 16.2763 11.4874 15.9835 11.7803L9.73346 18.0303C9.44056 18.3232 8.96569 18.3232 8.67279 18.0303Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></button></a></div></div></div></div></section><section data-slice-type="call_to_action_banner" data-slice-variation="default" class="bg-secondary-150"><div class="container py-20 lg:py-24"><div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-10 text-center lg:px-0"><div class="flex-1"><h2 class="text-26 lg:text-48 text-white">It’s easy to be compliant with CookieHub</h2><p class="mt-4 text-white">Sign up today and create a custom cookie banner for your website</p><div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:justify-center"><a href="/register?product_id=29"><button type="button" class="border-primary-100 bg-primary-100 border text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:outline-none hover:text-primary-100 focus:ring-primary-100 hover:bg-white bg-primary-100 uppercase rounded-md px-[25px] py-[12px] text-sm relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start">Start your 30 Day Free Trial</button></a><a href="/product"><button type="button" class="text-secondary-100 hover:text-secondary-125 border-transparent bg-transparent hover:text-secondary-125 bg-secondary-100 rounded-md px-[25px] py-[12px] text-sm !p-0 !text-base md:!text-lg relative flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center font-semibold tracking-[0.5px] transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out disabled:cursor-not-allowed md:w-auto md:justify-start hover:!text-primary-100 !p-2 text-white lg:ml-2">See all features</button></a></div></div></div></div></section></div><div class="divide-y-2 divide-gray-50 bg-white pt-16 pb-20 md:pt-32"><div class="container flex flex-col pb-8 lg:flex-row"><div class="order-2 mt-8 flex basis-full flex-col lg:order-1 lg:mt-0 lg:basis-1/4"><a href="/"><img alt="CookieHub Logo" loading="lazy" width="155" height="92" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="h-[92px]" style="color:transparent" src="/images/logo-footer.svg"/></a><div class="flex flex-row gap-4 py-6"><a aria-label="Change to English" href="https://www.cookiehub.com"><img alt="